{
  "texts": [
    "ResultsIn this section, we first report the network statistics computed at the node level from the three bipartite graphs in Sect. 4.1.",
    "Next, a diversity analysis examines how ESG topics are disclosed across companies and different sectors (Sect. 4.2).",
    "Section 4.3 reports company similarities according to jointly disclosed ESG actions.",
    "The follow-up section (4.4) addresses whether these company similarities are associated with similarities in other company information.",
    "Finally, we evaluate the interpretability of ESG scores by investigating the most impacting factual aspects (Sect. 4.5)."
  ]
}